strings.v: SOLO OBJECTIVES are now available! Earn special rewards by completing objectives! Some objectives are available for a limited-time only.
SOLO OBJECTIVES are special challenges which you can complete to earn rewards. Objectives come in the form of chains, which are made up of several related tasks.
Certain types of Objectives can be replaced. Tap to randomly replace your current Objective with a new one. This can be done for free once per day.
